      • ofType

        public static ColorMapper ofType​(int type,
                                 java.awt.Color from,
                                 java.awt.Color to)
        Creates a compatible color mapper.
        Parameters:
        type - image type, in same form as from BufferedImage
        from - source color
        to - target color
        Returns:
        a ColorMapper of appropriate type
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when image type is TYPE_CUSTOM, TYPE_BYTE_BINARY, TYPE_BYTE_GRAY, TYPE_USHORT_GRAY or unknown
